  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_6",
    "text": "影响孩子的学习",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.12998375203099613,
      0.31822222222222224,
      0.2839645044369454,
      0.3457777777777778
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_7",
    "text": "近视产生的视物模糊、眼睛干涩、酸痛、眼胀头晕、心烦气躁等，效率低，比 视力正常的孩子要多付出30％的学习时间。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1124859392575928,
      0.3582222222222222,
      0.8298962629671292,
      0.4142222222222222
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_8",
    "text": "影响升学和就业",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.12998375203099613,
      0.4275555555555556,
      0.2839645044369454,
      0.45422222222222225
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_9",
    "text": "高考升学电子信息、生物工程、医学制药、飞行、航海等近50多个专业报考受 限，许多单位及工种对近视有严格的限制。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1084864391951006,
      0.46755555555555556,
      0.8328958880139983,
      0.5235555555555556
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_11",
    "text": "影响日常生活",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.12998375203099613,
      0.5368888888888889,
      0.2634670666166729,
      0.5626666666666666
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_10",
    "text": "R",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7229096362954631,
      0.5386666666666666,
      0.9403824521934758,
      0.9937777777777778
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_12",
    "text": "近视儿童视物不清，给日常生活带来不便，如果佩戴眼镜，对体育 锻炼、打球、游泳、跑步都有影响，并可能受到伤害。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11498562679665042,
      0.5777777777777777,
      0.7189101362329708,
      0.6337777777777778
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_13",
    "text": "影响孩子的心理",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.12998375203099613,
      0.6453333333333333,
      0.2844644419447569,
      0.672
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_14",
    "text": "近视的孩子视物不清，影响对事物的认知，造成认知压力，担心近 视度数不断加深，有心理阴影，对外界对视力的评价敏感，对自信造成 压力等对孩子的心理健康造成很大的影响。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11148606424196976,
      0.6871111111111111,
      0.7239095113110862,
      0.7697777777777778
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_15",
    "text": "引起严重的井发症",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.13048368953880765,
      0.784,
      0.30696162979627545,
      0.8106666666666666
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_16",
    "text": "近视，尤其是高度近视，容易引起青光眼、玻璃体混浊、视网膜黄 斑、视网膜脱落甚至失明。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11098612673415822,
      0.824,
      0.7204099487564054,
      0.88
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_495_17",
    "text": "遗传后代",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
